Movie: The Worst Person in the World
Review: I found a piece of myself in every chapter/part of this film so much that my boyfriend said "she's exactly just like you" after seeing this with me.

Sabaw moment sa sinehan. Medyo nahirapan akong sundan yung first act and by the second act, nakatulog na ako. Tapos, naalimpungatan ako at nakalimutang nanonood ng horror so pagkamulat ko ang una kong nakita ay maraming dugo sa screen so nagsisigaw ako HAHAHAHAHA so nagsigawan din yung ibang mga nanonood.

Reminded me of a slightly similar experience I had with a guy I met in college. He was a graduating law student and I was a slightly disillusioned sophomore from a social science program. I had his number saved on my phone as Vanilla Darling Boy because our hookups were always slow and passionate as if we were making love on top of a glass that would collapse even with the slightest amount of pressure.Our thing went on forâ€¦
